="cddd8f83-8795-47bd-b6f6-1d8baa000459" class="r-5ohh77"><div data-rid="db12f62b-0cf4-413b-8dcb-f16efce2227e" class="r-1dn11uw"><div data-rid="5c61065c-3295-45ad-8b0d-801eaaeb2dce" class="r-1staxaf"><div data-rid="c65ea728-7e7a-40db-8fde-19bbe732557f" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-79878d61-29c3-4fdf-a61d-7ab28574c8d6-attributes-color-background-color:#EAC78BFF" class="r-1jzmmn1"><div data-rid="afcab2e4-b5f0-4d82-97a9-5b3f44e7c171" class="r-1cbzkfu alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-9543f1f4-fb33-41e1-907f-7d1894f1c1b1-attributes-color:#000000FF"><span style="width:100%"><p>1</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="146e2fde-f09e-42b7-9a9f-fd76011394da" class="r-1it3e1f alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>My Mom Was Exhausted And Nothing Helped Her</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="23f071ae-6263-4fd4-9267-5981b2a36bc2" class="r-1yf7aq4"><div data-rid="ae6d3a62-ebc3-4f19-ba67-81a0c0c18c83" class="r-omumxi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>She was in her mid-50s, going through menopause, and she couldn't sleep. Not "a little trouble falling asleep." I mean lying awake until 2, 3, sometimes 4 AM — exhausted but completely wired. Staring at the ceiling. Watching the clock. Waking up at 3 AM and not being able to get back down.</p><br><p>Her doctor put her on sleeping pills. They knocked her out — but she'd wake up feeling like an 18-wheeler hit her. Foggy, groggy, grumpy, worse than before. She tried melatonin. Gummies. Teas. Magnesium. Drink mixes. All of it. Some of it would knock her out, but none of it gave her <em>real</em> sleep.</p><br><p>She wasn't broken. The products were.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="40dc5bc7-3be2-4e53-8024-dc405eec2514" class="r-19qiw80"><div data-rid="d2e43136-94a6-4394-8004-6d1261fa4e7c" class="r-7zo3j8"><picture data-rid="2330fca5-9bee-4fc7-b4a9-1303aba48343" class="r-1yk8q8o"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/3175c11f-7a4b-445a-83d6-a6fd1172236d?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/3175c11f-7a4b-445a-83d6-a6fd1172236d?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/3175c11f-7a4b-445a-83d6-a6fd1172236d?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/3175c11f-7a4b-445a-83d6-a6fd1172236d" class="r-1ogdaqf" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="bf12d327-749d-49fb-90fb-2c2af2616d2d" class="r-1yrrdhb"><div data-rid="96561bf8-1181-41f1-8230-b569b9d56f86" class="r-1g7oo2q"><div data-rid="ed0870b5-fbd0-4c08-a647-00e4ef6ba681" class="r-8qedod"><div data-rid="ef39d8b6-e86c-459e-bd57-1bd557d656ff" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-79878d61-29c3-4fdf-a61d-7ab28574c8d6-attributes-color-background-color:#EAC78BFF" class="r-13235vg"><div data-rid="4524f0c4-03df-4104-ba9c-a31504642704" class="r-sn9jts alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-9543f1f4-fb33-41e1-907f-7d1894f1c1b1-attributes-color:#000000FF"><span style="width:100%"><p>2</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="b7b23152-e036-4e9e-a633-787be17ec946" class="r-19qbtdq alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>I Figured Out Why Nothing Worked And It Changed Everything</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="b71c0c24-5bbe-4afe-aa03-01351fc5bfe7" class="r-wmhim4"><div data-rid="bbfe306c-8faa-407f-9924-56227d29d7e0" class="r-umnkdt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I was a student at the University of Pennsylvania, watching my mom suffer through this, and I couldn't accept that there was no better answer. So I started researching.</p><br><p>What I found wasn't about ingredients — it was about <em>absorption</em>. Every pill, gummy, capsule, and tea on the market has the same fatal flaw: it has to survive your stomach. Your digestive system breaks it down over 60-90 minutes, destroying most of the active ingredients before they ever reach your bloodstream. You swallow a full dose and your body absorbs a fraction of it.</p><br><p>That's why the companies have to pack 10, 12 milligrams of melatonin into a gummy — they're compensating for how poorly it absorbs. And that's exactly why you wake up feeling drugged. You're not getting <em>better</em> sleep. You're getting <em>sedated</em>.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="000efbb4-f574-40ee-87cc-7cff57857df3" class="r-1bymo9x"><div data-rid="c64e08d2-5609-4cd7-978b-6309ba171c98" class="r-cevy5e"><picture data-rid="69a861d5-d7e1-485b-9f86-9e2de1104dd5" class="r-wdiss4"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/7ef0c4f7-3502-4b3d-8e74-3101b412ebfd?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/7ef0c4f7-3502-4b3d-8e74-3101b412ebfd?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/7ef0c4f7-3502-4b3d-8e74-3101b412ebfd?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/7ef0c4f7-3502-4b3d-8e74-3101b412ebfd" class="r-15hcmgw" loading="eager"/></picture></div><div data-rid="64353bb5-a3fd-4974-ba17-6081d19051d5" class="r-xqq4ig"><div data-rid="df505476-9864-4dc8-b3fd-38339f0e4bad" class="r-175xsj1"><div data-rid="2b6c5e51-51c5-4631-b48f-86668b63fe0d" class="r-13gcot2"><div data-rid="09a566c6-e212-42e4-96be-63a4a6bdc8ba" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-79878d61-29c3-4fdf-a61d-7ab28574c8d6-attributes-color-background-color:#EAC78BFF" class="r-q2t3o3"><div data-rid="90691e7a-02d2-4efc-89f1-78aa2670f0ae" class="r-1ty7p94 alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-9543f1f4-fb33-41e1-907f-7d1894f1c1b1-attributes-color:#000000FF"><span style="width:100%"><p>3</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="5226cf0a-6102-4425-a9fc-9e0f2f8dc7c5" class="r-gawvy alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>So I Made a Spray And It's Why It Actually Works</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="f05409ed-8b07-4580-b895-696c173dfecf" class="r-15g3eak"><div data-rid="82988cae-d3ce-43e0-bd54-2287ce8e128e" class="r-r8mk3l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Instead of a pill you swallow or a gummy you chew, I turned it into an oral spray. Six spritzes under your tongue.</p><br><p>Here's why that matters: under your tongue is one of the most absorbent surfaces in your body. It bypasses your digestive system entirely and goes straight into your bloodstream in minutes. Your body absorbs up to 60% more of the active sleep compounds compared to pills — which means we don't have to overload the formula to make it work. Every ingredient gets in, does its job, and doesn't linger.</p><br><p>That's why we tell everyone: use it just 10-15 minutes before bed. Because when this kicks in, it works fast.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4a3dcb94-916a-4cb6-9be4-b98ab