styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>She Stopped Waking Up at 3 AM</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="a195ea8b-5d47-4b96-8e12-e5e6809a1cbd" class="r-17yf0x0"><div data-rid="d58b1757-f4c2-4dca-bc35-8f1870728fa7" class="r-1heob2r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Falling asleep fast was only half the battle. The other half — the one that was really destroying her — was staying asleep.</p><br><p>Rejuvia is formulated with 13 all-natural ingredients including Passionflower, GABA, L-Theanine, Valerian Root, Chamomile, Magnesium, and Melatonin — each chosen specifically to support your full sleep cycle, not just knock you out for the first few hours. The result: you stay asleep through the night, through the important sleep cycles, so your body actually recovers.</p><br><p>For my mom, the 3 AM wake-ups stopped. For our 300,000+ customers, the math changes: fall asleep in 10-15 minutes instead of an hour, stay asleep through the night — that's 90+ more minutes of real, uninterrupted sleep every single night.</p></span></div></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b606fc07-caed-44ea-a793-e1cbc6bbd8ad" class="r-1fz528c"><div data-rid="264d277c-98f8-4431-a2ae-250572cf6dee" class="r-18hewhe"><picture data-rid="a25c88b5-6f99-4701-9ac4-99771e098e8c" class="r-gstfkr"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/cd18f480-1e52-40df-8057-6398081caa17?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/a6b9cd13-85b5-416b-9786-753e40672d80/cd18f4