tterspacing:-0.2px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><p>She Woke Up Feeling Like Herself Again</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="95d2325f-54c2-4120-9f99-d07e18f2f630" class="r-1y8nw09"><div data-rid="8c79895c-aaa9-4a24-882d-6fd3b400ed4d" class="r-j250jh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>This one mattered most to me.</p><p>The sleeping pills her doctor prescribed would knock her out — but she'd wake up foggy, confused, and feeling worse than before. That's because when you pack in high-dose melatonin or sedative compounds and run them through slow digestion, they're still lingering in your system when your alarm goes off.</p><br><p>Because Rejuvia absorbs fast and precisely, we don't need to overload the formula. The ingredients get into your system, get you to sleep, support you through the night, and by the time you wake up — they've done their job and cleared out. You wake up clear-headed, sharp, and actually ready for your day.</p><br><p>My mom went from waking up and feeling like a wreck to waking up and feeling like herself. That was the whole point.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="58ab1a0c-aca9-4554-b804-7c14a149574f" class="r-o0z9c"><picture data-rid="9ac0a6aa-8e10-4661-8d30-e4f6b2ecb680" class=